title: Club Friday The Series 15: Deepest Love
overview: Rey is a lesbian who's heartbroken when her ex Punpun leaves her for a man. Despite knowing that Nart himself is gay, Rey decides she wants to marry him, believing that her love for him would fix everything. Rey has to give up and accept that there are limits when it comes to love. She allows a third person, Songpol, to live in their house.
